description: I haven’t been able to attend ALT.NET Sydney or SydJS last month, as I had to follow up some family issues in Egypt on daily basis. However, Aaron Powell ( @slace) presented at SydJS last month, and was kind enough to record his talk on his laptop as a screencast and put it online.
